/// Bloom filter over byte keys with 2 hash functions derived from one
/// FNV-1a pass via double hashing: h_i = h1 + i * h2. insert sets bits in a
/// Vec<u64>; contains may yield false positives but never false negatives.
/// Document the false-positive trade-off of 2.
struct Bloom2 {
    bits: Vec<u64>,
